protein.specific_function: Involved in autophagy. Required for autophagosome formation. Target of the TOR kinase signaling pathway that regulates autophagy through the control of phosphorylation status of ATG13/KIAA0652 and ULK1, and the regulation of the ATG13-ULK1-RB1CC1 complex. Phosphorylates ATG13/KIAA0652. Involved in axon growth. Plays an essential role in neurite extension of cerebellar granule cells
